title: MainMenu - keyboard + mouse control
message:
MainMenu - keyboard + mouse control
*Adds focused buttons states as booleans in MainMenuScreen.
*Creates buttonPressed and focusedButton skins.
*Adds keyboard control over the main menu.
*Handles the navigation between widgets using the focused buttons states,
 the graphic effects being handled by setting the current focused button's
 style using focusedButton skin.
*Modifies MenuButton behavior so that when the mouse is over an widget,
 all the buttons will be defocused.
*Modifies the navigation of menu so that keyboard navigation is posible
 only when mouse doesn't focus any widget.
*Uses InputMultiplexer so input can be perceived by more than 1 class.
*Sets the text of the buttons more centered then before.
